<p>
<note n="0844003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0844003">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0845002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0845002">目＝因【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note>
<note n="0846001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0846001">善＝喜【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
